here.

181
00:09:21,269 --> 00:09:24,272
It's not right! Who does stuff
like that!?

182
00:09:24,314 --> 00:09:26,775
Huh!? How could you not know?!

183
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:30,236
Oh, come on. It wasn't all
that strange a thing to do.

184
00:09:30,278 --> 00:09:33,281
