and I was able to eat my fill on
just $1.

201
00:10:14,197 --> 00:10:18,201
You're a master of having fun
without having to spend a lot of
money!

202
00:10:18,243 --> 00:10:20,120
Indeed I am!

203
00:10:20,161 --> 00:10:23,581
But even so, the money we spent
today is a total fortune to the
common masses.

204
00:10:23,623 --> 00:10:25,917
[Tsumugi] It is?
[Ritsu] Pretty much.

205
00:10:25,959 --> 00:10:29,254
To tell you the truth, there
was this time last month when-

