drum sticks, this new sheet
music,

210
00:10:44,102 --> 00:10:45,770
and this new CD that just came
in?!

211
00:10:45,812 --> 00:10:48,064
Oh can I? Can I please?

212
00:10:48,106 --> 00:10:49,566
And then, out of the blue,

213
00:10:49,607 --> 00:10:52,569
that mean old Mio smacked me
upside the head, for no reason.

214
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:54,654
She smacked you?

215
00:10:58,324 --> 00:10:59,909
Is something the matter?

216
00:10:59,951 --> 00:11:03,121
[Tsumugi] Actually, there's
a favor that I'd like to ask
